    <td width="700" background="/lotr/gfx/cloud/bluecc.gif" height="15" valign="bottom"><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
        <tr><td><font face="Tolk, Times, serif" class="h1font"><font color="#8989B1">Intermediate Decks</font></B></font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td width="2"></td><td valign="top"> 
      <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5"><tr><td><font face="  Times, Times New Roman, serif" class="bfont"><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td colspan="2"><font face="Tolk, Times, serif" class="h1font">Isildurs Heir aka. Ranger-Sauron combination platter</font></td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Papy, Times, serif" class="h2font"> Rating</Font></TD><TD><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><font size=1>(4.50)</font> | <A HREF="/lotr/decks/decks.php?reviews=20332">Read Reviews</A></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Papy, Times, serif" class="h2font"> Author</font></TD><TD><font face="  Times, Times New Roman, serif" class="bfont"> <A HREF="http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=8523">Alexander "Eomer - RoR" Schwarz</A></FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Papy, Times, serif" class="h2font"> Description</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="  Times, Times New Roman, serif" class="bfont"> The new version of my Ranger deck, this time with a powerful Sauron Shadow.

</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Papy, Times, serif" class="h2font"> Submitted</Font></TD><TD><font face="  Times, Times New Roman, serif" class="bfont"> December 31, 2001</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Papy, Times, serif" class="h2font"> Cards</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="  Times, Times New Roman, serif" class="bfont"> Starting<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(175)">Frodo, Son of Drogo</a><br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(182)">The One Ring, The Ruling Ring</a><br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(191)">Arwen, Daughter of Elrond</a> (s)<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(260)">Legolas, Greenleaf</a> (s)<br>
<br>
Adventure Deck<br>
[1] Prancing Pony<br>
[2] <a href="javascript:card_browser(214)">Trollshaw Forest</a><br>
[3] <a href="javascript:card_browser(217)">Council Courtyard</a><br>
[4] Balins Tomb<br>
[5] Bridge of Khazad-Dum<br>
[6] Lothlorien Woods<br>
[7] <a href="javascript:card_browser(232)">Anduin Confluence</a><br>
[8] <a href="javascript:card_browser(235)">Anduin Banks</a><br>
[9] <a href="javascript:card_browser(242)">Summit of Amon Hen</a><br>
<br>
Free Peoples<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(245)">Aragorn, King in Exile</a> x3<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(306)">Boromir, Lord of Gondor</a> x3<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(193)">Sam, Son of Hamfast</a><br>
Aragorns Bow x2<br>
